sequenceDiagram
    actor Worker as Muncitor
    participant UI as Frontend React
    participant API as ActivityController
    participant Service as ActivityService
    participant InvRepo as InventoryItemRepository
    participant MachRepo as MachineryRepository
    participant CropRepo as CropSeasonRepository
    participant Notif as NotificationService
    participant DB as MySQL

    Worker->>UI: Completeaza raportul de finalizare
    UI->>API: PUT /api/activities/{id}/status
    API->>Service: updateActivityStatus(...)

    Service->>Service: verifica daca muncitorul este alocat
    Service->>Service: seteaza status COMPLETED
    Service->>Service: salveaza interval, comentarii si recolta

    Service->>InvRepo: preia produsele consumate
    InvRepo->>DB: SELECT inventory_items
    DB-->>InvRepo: produse
    InvRepo-->>Service: produse
    Service->>Service: valideaza consumurile reale
    Service->>DB: UPDATE stocuri si consumuri

    Service->>MachRepo: actualizeaza orele utilajelor
    MachRepo->>DB: UPDATE machinery

    alt lucrare de recoltare
        Service->>CropRepo: actualizeaza sau creeaza sezonul de cultura
        CropRepo->>DB: SELECT/INSERT/UPDATE crop_seasons
    end

    Service->>Notif: creeaza notificari pentru manager si agronom
    Notif->>DB: INSERT notifications

    Service->>DB: UPDATE activity
    DB-->>Service: activitate actualizata
    Service-->>API: raspuns succes
    API-->>UI: activitate finalizata
    UI-->>Worker: Taskul este marcat ca finalizat
